data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Light and Bright Beauty. Fresh paint, new carpet, new laminate flooring, painted cabinets, and a large yard are just a few things to point out in this 3 bed 2 bath Woodburn home. Possible dual living with primary bedrooms and living spaces on both floors. Large walk in closets in all bedrooms. .34 acres offer perimeter and cross fencing, established fruit trees, room for a garden, and a nice shed/work space. Located close to Woodburn Premium Outlets, grocery stores, swimming pool, and Interstate 5.
